citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 10:45am on
09-AUG-18.
Knocked on door-no answer. Left message on cell phone. Waited 30 min. Owner called back-out of town and
unavailable.
